<text top="247" left="252" width="911" height="64" font="font0" id="p1_t1" reading_order_no="0" segment_no="0" tag_type="text">And  technological  innovations  can  also  challenge </text>
<text top="305" left="206" width="957" height="57" font="font1" id="p1_t2" reading_order_no="1" segment_no="0" tag_type="text">us  profoundly.  Children  are  active,  mobile,  social </text>
<text top="351" left="205" width="957" height="65" font="font2" id="p1_t3" reading_order_no="2" segment_no="0" tag_type="text">beings  who  can  easily  find  their  way  into  violent  video </text>
<text top="403" left="205" width="958" height="65" font="font2" id="p1_t4" reading_order_no="3" segment_no="0" tag_type="text">games,  Web  sites  with  sexually  explicit  materials,  or </text>
<text top="455" left="205" width="959" height="65" font="font2" id="p1_t5" reading_order_no="4" segment_no="0" tag_type="text">chat  rooms  with  adults  posing  as  children.  Young </text>
<text top="508" left="204" width="960" height="65" font="font0" id="p1_t6" reading_order_no="5" segment_no="0" tag_type="text">people  can  also  be  subjected  to  computerized  library </text>
<text top="559" left="205" width="958" height="66" font="font2" id="p1_t7" reading_order_no="6" segment_no="0" tag_type="text">catalogues  that  make  it  almost  impossible  to  find  a </text>
